title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 9 2022

description:
New York Times journo says masks are sign of solidarity with minorities. Masters and Lake gaining momentum Arizona races. Mark Morgan, former acting commissioner of Customs and Border Protection joins Clay and Buck with a message to Republicans on the border. Thanks to everyone at KLBJ in Austin. Clay and Buck will be at Texas-Alabama game this weekend. Hilarious headline typo has Clay singing the national anthem at Sunday's Houston Texans game.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
